casebody.data:
No. 299,

Misc.

Iva Ikuko Toguri d’Aquino v. United States. Wayne M. Collins, George Olshausen and Marvel Shore for petitioner. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Mclnerney and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

C. A. 9th Cir. The motion for leave to file brief of Milton J. Jarvis and others, as amici curiae, is denied. Certiorari also denied.

Mr. Justice Clark took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
